title: Levi's 2014 Lunar New Year collection: New looks for a new y
description: The Levi's® 2014 Lunar New Year (Year of Horse) collection takes the pioneers of today on a journey that starts with the Modern Frontier, a belief that the wisdom gleaned from our past will allow for greater possibilities ahead. Be bold. Brave. Daring.
